### Ingestion Service - Submit Raw Medical Record
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/ingestion/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientName": "",
  "nationalId": "12345678901",
  "diseaseInfo": "Influenza",
  "hospitalName": "Ankara City Hospital"
}

### Get Record Status (Mock - DB lookup not yet implemented)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/ingestion/status/a1b2-track-001
Accept: application/json

### List Raw Records (Mock - 2 sample records)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/ingestion/records
Accept: application/json

### Cancel / Delete Record from Queue
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/ingestion/records/a1b2-track-001
Accept: application/json

### Service Health Check (Spring Boot Actuator)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

